---
/** Static “About” content with three parts:
 *  - Our Mission
 *  - How It Works (two subcards)
 *  - Join Us (CTA text + links)
 *
 */
---

<section class="container-page my-10 md:my-14">
    <div
      class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] backdrop-blur-xl
             shadow-2xl shadow-black/40 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-6 md:p-10 text-center"
    >
      <!-- Our Mission -->
      <header class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-wide">
            About UBC Game Dev
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-50/85">
          We are a student-run video game development club aiming to give students a hands-on
          approach in making video games and provide the tools needed to learn more about the industry.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-50/85">
          At UBC Game Development, we host a variety of workshops, invite industry guest-speakers, and hold
          regular meetings to help educate our members. We aim to give them the tools and knowledge to succeed
          in the art of video game development.
        </p>
      </header>
  
      <!-- How It Works -->
      <div class="mt-10">
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-wide">HOW IT WORKS</h3>
  
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <!-- Project Teams -->
          <article
            class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.05] p-5 md:p-6
                   ring-1 ring-white/10"
          >
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold">Project Teams</h4>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-50/85">
              Project Teams are led by experienced members and are balanced with a variety of skills to
              successfully design and develop an original game.
            </p>
          </article>
  
          <!-- Learning Community -->
          <article
            class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.05] p-5 md:p-6
                   ring-1 ring-white/10"
          >
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold">Learning Community</h4>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-50/85">
              The Learning Community is designed to foster a safe environment for aspiring developers to
              improve their skills, experiment, and make connections. Many members later join Project Teams
              once they feel confident in their skill development.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Join Us -->
      <div class="mt-10">
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-wide">Join Us</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-50/85">
          Interested in partnering or joining? Subscribe to our newsletter below and feel free to
          <a href="/contact" class="underline decoration-white/40 hover:decoration-[var(--brand)]">
            contact us
          </a>
          if you have any questions!
        </p>
        <!-- Optional CTAs; comment out if you only want text -->
        <!--
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="#subscribe" class="btn btn-outline rounded-full px-5 py-2">Subscribe</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline rounded-full px-5 py-2">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
        -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  